Fedora 20
=========
1) Install the following packages:
   python-devel
   gsl-devel 1.16 or later (1.15 and earlier have a cquad bug)
   gcc
   numpy
   scipy
   matplotlib
   
Ubuntu
======
1) Install the following packages:
   gcc
   python-dev
   python-numpy
   python-numpy-dev
   libgsl0ldbl
   libgsl0-dev
   python-scipy
   python-matplotlib
   python-futures



2) Run the command:
   python setup.py build

   and (add --user for local install)

   python setup.py install


   Binaries/scripts are found in /usr/local/bin or ~/.local/bin
   if --user is specified
